---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/url';
---
<Base title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How ReefMetric makes money — our FTC affiliate disclosure.">
  <section class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--brand-2)">Disclosure</p>
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p>ReefMetric is reader-supported. When you buy through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission — at no additional cost to you. These are “paid links.”</p>
    <p>We participate in affiliate programs including (as applicable) Bulk Reef Supply, Amazon Associates, Chewy, and other aquarium retailers and brands. As an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases.</p>
    <p>Commissions never influence our ratings, rankings, or which products we recommend. Our picks are determined by data, testing, and specs — not by which program pays more. If a product is the best choice, we say so whether or not we earn from it.</p>
    <p>Questions? <a href={url('/about')}>Learn more about how we work</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
